{"tid":1891662,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"絕 - 沖入狗屋毒撚死你 #樓主死毒撚標題黨 #的士陳 x 飯聚人士","createTime":"2020-02-22T04:18:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-22T11:18:46.000Z","uid":340729,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"fb61bfb943d40895eb29f87f3efb0128ee904e54","tid":1891662,"uid":340729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T04:18:06.000Z","msg":"整合:<br />\n其實滯留在警處<br />\n無奈播毒踏的士<br />\n有咳嗽報案實時<br />\n有咳嗽也會瀨屎<br />\n留條命才是不智<br />\n故此沖入做傻事<br />\n讓細菌 傳人千次<br />\n彰顯那播毒無盡時<br />\n<br />\n肺閪人道毀滅<br />\n殺掉我跟狗<br />\n我不含毒性<br />\n背負毛澤神經症<br />\n<br />\n狂咳已漸逝<br />\n全警署食滯<br />\n強哥我話你直頭全亡<br />\n原地槍斃<br />\n年頭就生仔 濃痰就一世<br />\n冚家爆未世共同存亡<br />\n自殺針劑<br />\n<br />\n還不夠食滯 被天殺絕誓<br />\n全家葬十次用來形容林鄭&quot;木&quot;契<br />\n還我正義 謝絕肺炳強<br />\n返堔圳就係需即刻殮葬<br />\n<br />\n存在為求是生化<br />\n我對咳血沒期望<br />\n被爆肛<br />\n傳人釋放<br />\n明知道絕後<br />\n就不應該插我<br />\n能夠這樣<br />\n全靠你幫忙<br />\n將警察絕後的標準答案<br />\n<br />\n潮文/創作背景:<br />\n今次主人公好慘呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上左架肺炎的士 中左肺武 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n主人公咳左一聲之後 發現自己唔得喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就馬上有報狗既念頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢走到狗屋門口 俾人拉左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又瀨屎瀨尿放飛劍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲因此俾gay警爆左後庭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幾日之後 狗隻就中左肺炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再加上飯聚 仲惹埋炳炳<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我係唔係傻左?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢一句:肺閪人道毀滅 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後 全香港黑警死曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為呢個故事就係當年既旺角阿伯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59f6836dfcd17763874130f48cd029b413f1b85a","tid":1891662,"uid":340729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T04:19:31.000Z","msg":"打漏左公程式"},{"pid":"aa0b2ee9f786bd0aa99bb65248d1c4bca2ac5f4d","tid":1891662,"uid":340729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T04:28:25.000Z","msg":"原post<br />\n絕(黑警肺炎版)<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/fcisuS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/fcisuS</a>"},{"pid":"7545c8e2412ad9d724fbdba723fb258dfb5f1dd5","tid":1891662,"uid":44795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T04:36:57.000Z","msg":"推到有人唱<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78081d4c8d641da9f31bc4c2030ef6a1d88f9c89","tid":1891662,"uid":340729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7545c8e2412ad9d724fbdba723fb258dfb5f1dd5","tid":1891662,"uid":44795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T04:36:57.000Z","msg":"推到有人唱<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T04:55:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56b8d23785937a85991971c79e5a1f440ba7851a","tid":1891662,"uid":340729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T05:30:24.000Z","msg":"無人打賞 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"177634725acfaf3f4656ae0204232b2655905d0f","tid":1891662,"uid":44795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T11:18:46.000Z","msg":"推"}],"pinned":{"pid":"59f6836dfcd17763874130f48cd029b413f1b85a","tid":1891662,"uid":340729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T04:19:31.000Z","msg":"打漏左公程式"}}